<h2 id="when-not-to-use-the-header">When not to use the header</h2>

<p>Do not use a header unless your websie is part of the Essex.gov.uk domain.</p>

<h2 id="how-to-use-the-header">How to use the header</h2>

<p>The header is displayed at the top of every page and is consistent across the entire site.</p>

<p>It should display the siteâ€™s identity and branding, making it clear to the user what website they are on.</p>
